properties.name: Dallas, Texas
properties.description: Posted by EriktukumsDallas is a big city in Texas. Dallas as a plethera of attractions in area\'s of art and sports. The Dallas Museum of Art is a museum filled of activities like jazz, dinner, and wine tastings. Dallas also has a wide-range in sports like the Dallas Cowboys and the Dallas Mavericks. Lastly at the Texas Fair has many fun things to do like an opportunity to win a car, robeo\'s, and a bird show.

properties.name: Jackson, Mississippi
properties.description: Posted by EriktukumsThis is a city in Mississippi. Filled of recreational and fun activity places to visit. There is even a planetarium which holds many people and shows pictures of the universe very clearly. They also have a very big zoo called The Jackson Zoological Park which holds a diverse amount of animals.

properties.name: Mexico City. Mexico
properties.description: Posted by EriktukumsMexico City is one of the major cities in Mexico. Mexico City not only is built over an ancient city but has many museams and recrational areas in the city. This city has an array of cultural activities thanks to its ancient roots. It also has over 100 museams.

properties.name: Monterrey, Mexico
properties.description: Posted by EriktukumsMonterrey is an industerious city in Mexico. It is also surprisingly a great tourist attraction filled of "day activities". Some "day activities" are water parks at the Plaza Sésamo, the nature adventures like the Skyline tour and the Outdoor tours. There are also many night-time activites like the Open Air Concerts at the Marco Plaza and the "Beer Garden" at the Cerveceria Cuauhtemoc Moctezuma.
